---
title: Rosemary Glazed Chicken with Purple Mash and Buttered Leeks
description: Our chef André loves a classic dish with a twist. What could be more classic than roast chicken, where is the twist you may ask? Well have you ever had roast chicken with purple mashed potato? We thought not! We think this dish is even better than the classic!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rosemary-glazed-chicken-with-pur-6682a208.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/rosemary-glazed-chicken-with-pur-93d49ed2.pdf
nutrition:
  calories: 615 kcal
  fat: 27 g
  saturated fat: 16 g
